Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:06.44,DBZ Standard,000,0,0,0,,{\fad(532,532)}{\pos(325,100)}FIST OF THE NORTH STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:06.44,DBZ Standard,000,0,0,0,,{\fad(532,532)}{\pos(325,275)}TV COMPILATION 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:06.44,DBZ Standard,000,0,0,0,,{\fad(532,532)}Six Sacred Fists of Nanto!\NRei, the Star of Justice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:24.12,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:33.73,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up! Come on, lady!\NLet's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.40,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Wait up, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.73,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Whoa, she's a pretty one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.13,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' excited already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.63,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,We've got a lot of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.23,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Play nice with us\Nand we'll give you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.40,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:13.67,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Then I'll just take it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.41,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Y- You're a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.68,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Whenever I disguise\Nmyself as a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.52,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,perverts like you\Ninevitably show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.12,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,But you people do\Nserve a purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:35.29,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,because you always\Nbring food to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.16,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Oh, gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.03,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.64,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,My name?\NMy name is Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.04,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Rei of the {\i1}Nanto Suichoken{\i0} school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:50.04,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nanto Suichoken{\i0} school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:52.01,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,- Why, you...!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.91,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.68,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,It really is!\N{\i1}Nanto Suichoken{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:29.21,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,The South Star Water Bird Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.62,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its movements are{\i0}\N{\i1}supposedly as graceful...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.52,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,{\i1}as those of a bird{\i0}\N{\i1}floating on the water!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:39.86,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, its power and cruelty as{\i0}\N{\i1}a killing technique are unmatched!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:43.53,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Oh...? You seem to know\Na bit about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:49.37,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,You have to be strong if you\Nexpect to survive in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.57,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,No one has ever been able\Nto stand up to my nunchakus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.44,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Then I'll be the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.44,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:10.62,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Take that! And that!\NAnd that! And... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.33,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,You dropped these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:27.17,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,You cannot counter my movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.41,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:36.48,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,Do you know a man with\Nseven scars on his chest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.88,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,N-N-N-NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:41.62,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,I see... Then I have\Nno further use for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.72,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,I'll take care of\Nthat food you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,NARRATION,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.65,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man With Seven Scars...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:10.12,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until I kill you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:13.32,DBZ Standard,023,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll even eat mud to survive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,NARRATION,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.63,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,This belongs to my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:21.03,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,My sister Airi was to\Nwear this for her wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:25.34,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, the night{\i0}\N{\i1}before Airi's wedding...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:56.86,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,Bandits attacked my village while\NI was away. They killed my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.27,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,And took away Airi, who was\Nfinally going to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.41,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.42,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,Airi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.36,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what{\i0}\N{\i1}the man looks like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.44,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,but with his last breath,\Nmy father told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.84,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,he had seven scars\Non his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:35.64,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,Airi may already be dead...\NBut I don't think she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:39.28,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,I can see her even now!\NHer face stained with tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.01,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,I can hear her calling\Nfor me even now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:46.42,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,I swear I'll find the\Nman with seven scars...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.32,DBZ Standard,025,0,0,0,,And then kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.71,DBZ Standard,027A,0,0,0,,Airi, it's me! I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:37.08,DBZ Standard,027A,0,0,0,,Who? Who is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:41.95,DBZ Standard,027A,0,0,0,,A- Airi...\NYou're still alive, Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.76,DBZ Standard,027A,0,0,0,,Calm down, Rei!\NDon't go any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:52.06,DBZ Standard,027A,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.50,DBZ Standard,027A,0,0,0,,Rei! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.07,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,LET ME GO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.11,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Airi! Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.09,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:16.06,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,It's the veil you were going to\Nwear for your wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.80,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,{\i1}This embroidery...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.64,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Can it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.44,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.34,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Yes! Airi, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.57,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:41.75,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,I thought I'd never see\Nmy brother again in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:45.62,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,If I knew I could, then I...\NI never would have lost hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.92,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:03.51,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,After it happened,\NI had nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:09.08,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was sold again and again{\i0}\N{\i1}as a slave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:15.22,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despair... That's all I had left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.46,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't have the courage{\i0}\N{\i1}to choose death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:27.46,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,{\i1}So my only way to live in this world{\i0}\N{\i1}was to close my mind to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.37,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.31,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:38.38,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Big Brother, where are you?!\NCome to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:39.88,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.84,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,- Big Brother!\N- Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.98,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.69,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,What are you...?!\NGET OUT OF MY WAY!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:05.87,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.40,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:16.71,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,AIRI!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.45,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.12,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,AIRI!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:31.39,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,Your dear sister\Nis now in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:41.37,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,How dare you kill\Nmy beloved sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.91,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,S- Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:49.71,DBZ Standard,027B,0,0,0,,I want you all to\Nknow the pain I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.00,DBZ Standard,028A,0,0,0,,Try it blindfolded now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.86,DBZ Standard,028A,0,0,0,,- Now with the other girl.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.08,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Wait, please!\NI'll do anything you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.74,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Just don't kill Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:40.71,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,In that case...\NKill the {\i1}Hokuto{\i0} man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:41.82,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.42,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Calm down, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.05,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,They're trying to kill\None of us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.06,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Don't let them get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.29,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Think what would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.83,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,if the {\i1}Nanto{\i0} and {\i1}Hokuto{\i0} schools\Nfought each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.94,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,What will you do, {\i1}Nanto{\i0} man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:07.64,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.44,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.35,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Do it, {\i1}Nanto{\i0} man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:19.89,DBZ Standard,028B,0,0,0,,Destroy the follower of {\i1}Hokuto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:24.63,DBZ Standard,028C,0,0,0,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.77,DBZ Standard,028D,0,0,0,,I just... I just don't\Nwant to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.38,DBZ Standard,028D,0,0,0,,But I have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:52.88,DBZ Standard,028E,0,0,0,,Rei! Unless you use all your skills,\Nyou'll never kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:57.55,DBZ Standard,028E,0,0,0,,That stance... The legendary\NNorth Star Ultimate Holy Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.59,DBZ Standard,028E,0,0,0,,You know what this\Nstance means, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.51,DBZ Standard,028E,0,0,0,,What's up?\NThey ain't movin' at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.75,DBZ Standard,028E,0,0,0,,You don't know just\Nhow intense this battle is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.82,DBZ Standard,028E,0,0,0,,They're both guarding\Nthemselves so carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.79,DBZ Standard,028E,0,0,0,,that neither one\Nof them can attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.30,DBZ Standard,028F,0,0,0,,South Star Tiger Beating Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.73,DBZ Standard,028F,0,0,0,,North Star Dragon Attacking Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.81,DBZ Standard,028F,0,0,0,,Watch carefully. Those stances show\Nthey're betting their lives on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:51.31,DBZ Standard,028F,0,0,0,,The winner will be decided\Nin the next instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:20.81,DBZ Standard,028G,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.56,DBZ Standard,028G,0,0,0,,As I thought...\NWe beat each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.76,DBZ Standard,028G,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ken! Rei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.10,DBZ Standard,028G,0,0,0,,They're both dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.81,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,Kemada, Gibara...\NMy dear sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.94,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,You have been avenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.68,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.22,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,We're leaving!\NNow kill the women!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.33,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,Stay back, you monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.64,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,What the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:23.64,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,Father!\NFather, those guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.18,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,What about them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.64,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,They're... They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:31.48,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,They're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:39.99,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.43,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.06,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,You tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.41,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,Deceiving your\Nenemies to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.63,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,is also a technique\Nof our fighting styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.71,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,The Ultimate Holy Ring\Nstance was a signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.87,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,to attack each other's\Npower points to simulate death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.88,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.68,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,You villains don't\Ndeserve fair play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:08.85,DBZ Standard,028H,0,0,0,,You were in Death's grip\Nfrom the very start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.73,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Mountain Splitting Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,NARRATION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.71,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,The Fang Clan's been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.61,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Now nobody will\Nthreaten our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:47.21,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Light! Light has\Nreturned to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.43,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,I guess this means\Nour job's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.03,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,What will you do now, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:09.54,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Find a nice, quiet\Nplace to live with Airi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.21,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:16.30,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Looks like I owe you\Nanother big debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.17,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,By the way, Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.88,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,are you going to stop looking\Nfor the man with seven scars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:24.35,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:33.26,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,You killed a lot of people\Nso you could kill him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.94,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th- This is...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.95,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Ken, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.66,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.57,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.33,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.61,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Airi, you can...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:30.12,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,I can see. It's still a little fuzzy,\Nbut I can see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.82,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.19,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,- Big Brother!\N- Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.42,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:46.03,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Ken, even if you told me you were\Nthe one who took Airi away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.47,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,I wouldn't believe it.\NI know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:57.44,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,Hey, Mamiya, what's up?\NWhat are you doing in a dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.61,DBZ Standard,029,0,0,0,,What?! You jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:35.64,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,NARRATION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:31.98,DBZ Standard,044,0,0,0,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:34.55,DBZ Standard,044,0,0,0,,Ken-Oh's squad is attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:40.82,DBZ Standard,044,0,0,0,,Ken-Oh's squad?\NAiri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:56.69,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:05.34,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,There's still one runt left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:11.08,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:20.08,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Even children must swear\Nloyalty to Ken-Oh-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:24.56,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Brand yourself with his crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.77,0:22:33.38,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, maybe\Nwe'll have you dance on that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:35.85,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,until you're\Nburned to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:38.94,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:49.39,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,So, what will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:54.09,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:23:02.30,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,I'll never obey devils like\Nyou who prey on the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:06.40,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:09.57,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,You've got guts,\Nyou little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:22.19,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will not obey a demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:52.07,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Want a hand, little lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:56.59,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,No need to be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:00.96,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:06.23,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:10.03,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,What's with you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:12.96,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,You're a demon in human guise!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:15.06,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:26.91,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the South Star{\i0}\N{\i1}Waterfowl Fist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:28.48,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.29,0:24:32.85,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Lin! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:35.06,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Hey! Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:37.97,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,Hey, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.61,0:24:42.04,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,You demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.61,0:24:46.08,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,You'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:47.80,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.28,0:24:51.41,DBZ Standard,045,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.26,0:25:05.62,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,The fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.99,0:25:09.45,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,If my stomach\Nignites, I'll blow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.66,0:25:12.86,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,Help m...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.64,0:25:19.13,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,{\i1}How pathetic...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.62,0:25:33.48,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,- Ken-Oh-sama!\N- Ken-Oh-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.63,0:25:47.00,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,This is Ken's older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.53,0:25:51.40,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,You must be Ken-Oh... no,\NKenshiro's older brother, Raoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.54,0:25:53.66,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,So you're Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.37,0:25:58.71,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,It was a pleasure watching\Nyour South Star Waterfowl Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.38,0:26:03.51,DBZ Standard,046,0,0,0,,Then I'll show you the essence\Nof my techniques as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.45,0:26:07.08,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I'll ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.32,0:26:11.55,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Have you seen the star\Nadjacent to the Big Dipper?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.52,0:26:13.49,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.39,0:26:15.36,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.56,0:26:20.69,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I see. Then you must have been\Ndestined to fight against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.17,0:26:24.29,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Very well. Go ahead\Nand attack as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.57,0:26:26.44,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,What? You won't dismount?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.51,0:26:32.31,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Do you think that I stand on\Nequal ground with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.48,0:26:34.54,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,There is no man\Nleft in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.68,0:26:37.24,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,who can force me\Nto stand on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.52,0:26:39.78,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Then you can die\Ntogether with your horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.49,0:26:45.65,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,South Star Ultimate Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.82,0:26:48.32,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Self-Sacrifice\NCounterbalance Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.76,0:26:51.42,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone, lend{\i0}\N{\i1}me your strength!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.85,0:27:19.31,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's going to try to{\i0}\N{\i1}kill us both!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.56,0:27:22.69,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,South Star Ultimate Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.90,0:27:25.42,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Self-Sacrifice\NCounterbalance Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.60,0:27:33.09,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Saw right through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.41,0:27:36.31,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,You've seen the\NDeath Omen Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.32,0:27:44.98,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,- Rei!\N- Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.27,0:28:09.37,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.21,0:28:14.11,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.48,0:28:18.58,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,So you came, Kenshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.38,0:28:20.37,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Raoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.62,0:28:22.61,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.40,0:28:31.36,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.56,0:28:35.57,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Kenshiro, it's a wonder\Nyou've survived to this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.57,0:28:37.83,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,with your naive\Nviews on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:42.61,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,For that, I praise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.61,0:28:46.10,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,But those caught up\Nby passion will inevitably...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.28,0:28:48.54,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.08,0:28:52.28,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.85,0:28:56.12,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,- Rei!\N- Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.46,0:28:58.42,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.96,0:29:01.93,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.63,0:29:04.62,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Why didn't you\Nwait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.90,0:29:09.93,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Rei wanted to repay\Nhis debt to you, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.00,0:29:13.70,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.\NJust for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.29,0:29:24.66,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Ken, stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.87,0:29:31.83,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.38,0:29:44.14,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Does this face look like it's\Ngoing to his death?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.38,0:29:49.22,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.05,0:29:52.04,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.90,0:30:27.67,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,You look like you might\Nbe stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.94,0:30:31.50,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,But it seems like your naivety\Nhas not changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.75,0:30:35.58,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Go ahead and try me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.22,0:30:37.88,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I'll also ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.12,0:30:42.65,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Have you seen the star\Nadjacent to the Big Dipper?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.06,0:30:45.25,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,No. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.36,0:30:50.66,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Then, that means it is not the\Ntime for us to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.96,0:30:55.13,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Where do you think your going? I'll\Nsettle this with you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.37,0:30:57.53,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Don't push your luck, Kenshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.26,0:31:25.32,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,{\i1}This giant aura, it's much greater{\i0}\N{\i1}than what Raoh used to have!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.51,0:31:35.95,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll grant your\Nwish and take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.02,0:31:40.92,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Come, Kenshiro.\NShow me how much you've grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.33,0:31:50.76,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,You shall see it\Nthrough with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.24,0:31:56.20,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.14,0:32:05.17,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I can see your fighting\Nspiritual energy clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.51,0:32:07.85,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,You've mastered it quite well...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.76,0:32:25.23,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.67,0:32:26.63,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,The air...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.83,0:32:29.20,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,The air is being\Ndrawn towards them!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.86,0:32:53.38,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,A tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.14,0:33:10.11,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.51,0:33:12.57,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Look, above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.18,0:33:32.15,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.45,0:33:37.41,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,If this was night, you would\Nclearly see the Death Omen Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.46,0:33:51.26,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Learn how to fight off\Nof your damn horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.47,0:33:55.87,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,North Star Seven\NDeaths Cavalry Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.44,0:34:01.41,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.16,0:34:24.79,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,You've scarred me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.10,0:34:29.37,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I told you,\NI'm not the man I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.74,0:34:31.54,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Get off the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.68,0:34:38.11,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,You fool, you still don't\Nrealize that your life was spared?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.41,0:34:39.38,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.69,0:34:45.95,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.16,0:34:48.21,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,This arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.66,0:34:51.15,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,If someone hadn't\Nhit me with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.13,0:34:54.96,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.44,0:35:02.34,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,You over there, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.88,0:35:16.82,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Rei, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.95,0:35:19.32,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Ken, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.69,0:35:22.66,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.39,0:35:24.69,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,- Brother!\N- Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.16,0:35:29.83,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,- Rei...\N- Rei, you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.80,0:35:33.60,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I thought you\Nwere a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.64,0:35:35.60,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.74,0:35:40.57,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,So you're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.98,0:35:42.47,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.21,0:35:46.91,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I gave that man\Nthree days to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.48,0:35:48.45,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.05,0:35:51.14,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Valiant warriors who defy me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.45,0:35:54.25,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I don't kill such\Nexperts immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.49,0:35:55.65,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.96,0:35:59.05,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,If you kill too quickly,\Nthe fear will not spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.33,0:36:01.89,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,But fighters\Nwith three days to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.13,0:36:06.63,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,will tremble in fear of death,\Ngrieve, and suffer to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.94,0:36:10.74,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,Soon that terror\Nturns to legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.04,0:36:14.50,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,And the name Ken-Oh\Ncarries all the more weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.84,0:36:19.34,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,I've hit his pressure\Npoint, "Shinkesshu."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.51,0:36:23.25,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,In three days, blood will erupt\Nfrom all over his dying body.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.52,0:36:26.09,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,In the meantime,\Nhe can taste the terror...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.09,0:36:29.65,DBZ Standard,047,0,0,0,,of death that looms\Ncloser by the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.35,0:36:40.31,DBZ Standard,050,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.04,0:37:47.17,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,This emblem\Non your shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.04,0:37:50.53,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,- No!\N- Mamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.14,0:37:53.98,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,- That's...\N- It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.21,0:37:55.98,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,UD! It's Yuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.22,0:37:59.48,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,She was one of Yuda's women?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.85,0:38:03.48,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,Poor thing, she must\Nhave been through hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.26,0:38:10.49,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,Mamiya, why is there a Yuda\Nemblem on your shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.70,0:38:17.60,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,That man took\Nmy future from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.07,0:38:20.60,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,He condemned me to\Nfighting for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.14,0:38:24.51,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,This scar...\NIt will never go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.65,0:38:28.98,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,Much like the\Nscars in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.12,0:38:31.08,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,Mamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.92,0:38:34.18,DBZ Standard,051,0,0,0,,Rei, don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.87,0:38:50.84,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Mamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,NARRATION
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.61,0:38:56.74,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.28,0:38:58.61,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.58,0:39:00.60,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.39,0:39:09.91,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,This way, you have\Nno reason to come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.11,0:39:40.24,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Rei! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.35,0:39:42.32,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.52,0:39:43.49,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Ke...Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.52,0:39:47.52,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Looks like the medicine\Nfrom Medicine City
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.52,0:39:49.32,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,isn't working too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.53,0:39:52.03,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,You are going to defeat\NYuda, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.03,0:39:55.76,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know him.\NI know Yuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.80,0:39:58.96,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,We're both men\Nof the South Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.27,0:40:00.24,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.37,0:40:04.07,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,He's one of the South\NStar Six Sacred Fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.67,0:40:08.48,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,There are four other masters\Nof the South Star Sacred Fists
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.48,0:40:11.04,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,besides your friend Shin and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.35,0:40:16.01,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Six men stand atop the 108 styles\Nof the South Star Sacred Fist styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.19,0:40:19.28,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,They are known as the South\NStar Six Sacred Fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.76,0:40:22.99,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Yuda... he's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.93,0:40:25.12,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Yuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.36,0:40:30.93,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,I have two days left to live.\NI won't seek Mamiya's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.87,0:40:37.54,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,I only want to die for her\Nand live on in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.58,0:40:44.48,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,In the age we live in,\Nthe lives of men are short.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.42,0:40:49.38,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,But women will have children\Nand pass on their tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.75,0:40:54.45,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,The tales of brave men\Nand their battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.53,0:40:59.46,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,Yuda... you're a worthy trophy\Nfor my final moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.86,0:41:02.16,DBZ Standard,052,0,0,0,,I'll defeat him,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.71,0:42:14.71,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.33,0:41:22.88,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.36,0:41:27.33,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Mamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.87,0:41:31.30,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,I'm sure the scar on\Nyour shoulder is still intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.90,0:41:32.87,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Yuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.08,0:41:41.53,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Mamiya, it seems that you too,\Ncan see the Death Omen Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.01,0:41:46.28,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,I hold the key\Nto that death.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.96,0:41:58.40,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Just like the fate of your\Nfamily rested in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.97,0:42:06.16,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Your blood will surely\Nmake me even more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.94,0:42:11.77,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Now, would you be so kind\Nto guide me to Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.80,0:42:22.33,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Rei, you still haven't\Nrotted away?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.77,0:42:26.67,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Yuda... I'm impressed to\Nsee you come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.71,0:42:31.34,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,I just came here to witness your\Nanaemic style first hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.75,0:42:34.01,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,And to extinguish\Nthe Star of Justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.22,0:42:36.71,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,with the Star of Enchantment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.15,0:42:38.98,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,You're a sad\Nand pathetic fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.15,0:42:44.79,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,devoting your final moments\Nto one lousy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.56,0:42:51.30,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,To a woman branded by me\Nwithout a tomorrow to speak of!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.61,0:43:03.24,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Is that all you\Nhave to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.65,0:43:06.98,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Even if Mamiya\Nis destined to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.72,0:43:09.55,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,my feelings will not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.59,0:43:12.75,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Mamiya... a sad woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.59,0:43:17.92,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,At least let there be one man\Nwilling to die just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.83,0:43:21.73,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Crying over a woman?\NHow spineless, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.20,0:43:25.86,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Yuda... let's settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.48,0:43:31.28,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,South Star Crimson Crane Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.52,0:43:33.28,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,South Star Waterfowl Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.42,0:44:08.22,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,South Star Waterfowl Fist!\NFlight of the Red Sparrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.47,0:44:22.50,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,What gives you\Nso much power...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.11,0:44:28.05,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,What drives me is my love\Nfor Mamiya. It burns in my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.08,0:44:31.05,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,You wouldn't understand\Na thing about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.02,0:44:32.99,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,This is it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.85,0:44:37.76,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Yuda, today, the Star of\NEnchantment will fall to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.99,0:44:43.02,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,You think you've defeated me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.67,0:44:47.57,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Fool! No one can beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.10,0:44:50.30,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Not even you,\Nthe Star of Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.31,0:44:54.47,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Yuda's up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.84,0:44:57.78,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Yeah... Be careful, Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.38,0:45:01.54,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,My star shines with\Nbeauty and wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.62,0:45:04.28,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Do you think I came\Nwithout a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.59,0:45:05.55,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.79,0:45:08.76,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,I can hear it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.02,0:45:11.08,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Soon, you'll see hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.00,0:45:20.33,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.01,0:45:30.50,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,- What's wrong?\N- What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.22,0:45:36.18,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.49,0:46:13.39,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,What are you\Ntrying to pull, Yuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.59,0:46:15.25,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Did you break the dam?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.33,0:46:18.29,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.39,0:46:22.35,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,This sandy ground will turn\Nto quicksand and suck people in!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.53,0:46:24.33,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Well? Now you can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.57,0:46:27.07,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,The South Star Waterfowl Fist's\Nsecret techniques...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.07,0:46:28.87,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,lie in intricate footwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.07,0:46:32.17,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Now that your lower\Nbody is stuck in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.41,0:46:34.88,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,you're like a waterfowl\Nwith no wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.08,0:46:37.44,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,You will die an ugly\Ndeath in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.75,0:46:40.72,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.95,0:46:49.98,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,The Star of Enchantment shines\Nmore beautifully in red!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.69,0:46:57.53,DBZ Standard,055,0,0,0,,The pathetic Star of Justice\Nwill fall in this ugly mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.04,0:47:02.94,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Every step that I get\Ncloser, I'll slice you deeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.55,0:47:08.71,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Cut, cut, cut, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.18,0:47:47.02,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fight freely to{\i0}\N{\i1}your heart's content.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.50,0:48:03.63,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Tell me, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.34,0:48:08.30,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Who's the strongest and the\Nmost beautiful in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.84,0:48:12.14,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, then.\NIt's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.68,0:48:16.81,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,I, Yuda-sama, am the strongest\Nand the most beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.08,0:48:19.05,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.12,0:48:23.95,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei, you can't lose!\NDon't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.06,0:48:29.59,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei of the Star of Justice.\NYou're just a pathetic clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.93,0:48:32.52,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,You couldn't even\Nsave one woman's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.87,0:48:39.13,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,One more step!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.37,0:48:41.84,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,One more step\Nand you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.77,0:48:43.80,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.93,0:48:45.93,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.87,0:49:09.83,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,The water...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.60,0:49:12.73,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,The water has stopped flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.37,0:49:18.10,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,The Star of Deception\Nshines in the southern sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.34,0:49:19.33,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Here's the finishing strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.94,0:49:21.97,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,South Star Crimson Crane Fist\Nsecret technique:
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.11,0:49:23.24,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Blood-Tainted Beak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.99,0:49:39.99,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.15,0:49:49.09,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,South Star Waterfowl Fist\Nsecret technique:
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.32,0:49:50.95,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Soaring White Splendor!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.63,0:49:56.60,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.67,0:50:00.63,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.37,0:50:09.60,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,You can't defeat me, Yuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.18,0:50:14.15,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.95,0:50:16.38,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,The battle's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.32,0:50:22.19,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,I won't die like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.66,0:50:25.29,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Not like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.12,0:50:40.61,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,The man who's stronger,\Nmore beautiful than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.50,0:50:56.49,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Yuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.98,0:51:06.21,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,- Yuda-sama!\N- Yuda-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.49,0:51:13.86,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Ever since my heart\Nwas drawn to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.06,0:51:17.52,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,the Star of Deception has been\Ndestined to be extinguished
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.67,0:51:19.43,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,by the Star of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.07,0:51:21.04,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Yuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.57,0:51:25.01,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei... you were the only man\NI've ever respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.21,0:51:30.04,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,The strongest and the most\Nbeautiful man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.93,0:51:45.73,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,At least, just let me\Ndie in your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.68,0:51:59.70,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Yuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.75,0:52:05.37,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Yuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.80,0:52:20.89,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Yuda, you too were\Na lonely warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.77,0:52:24.07,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,But I'll be joining you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.38,0:52:34.78,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Farewell, South Star\NSix Sacred Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.78,0:52:37.75,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,The Crimson Crane Fists' Yuda,\Nof the Star of Deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.29,0:52:43.05,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Why do they have to spill\Neach other's blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.29,0:52:46.39,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Somehow, something's\Ngone wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.53,0:52:54.76,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Mamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.64,0:53:04.61,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Mami-
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.65,0:53:08.62,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.22,0:53:12.19,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.29,0:53:18.59,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Looks like my\Ntime's finally up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.79,0:53:19.76,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.99,0:53:23.46,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Mamiya. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.83,0:53:27.79,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Live your life to the fullest\Nuntil the Death Omen Star falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.07,0:53:33.47,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Even if just for a moment,\Nlive as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.04,0:53:36.14,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Pursue a woman's happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.02,0:53:52.19,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.96,0:53:58.02,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.17,0:54:00.36,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.17,0:54:03.26,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,You must not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.97,0:54:06.31,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,You're the last person\Nthat I would have
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.31,0:54:09.28,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,witness me crumble away\Nand die so pathetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.41,0:54:13.38,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.96,0:54:33.63,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,May you be happy, Mamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.71,0:54:43.23,DBZ Standard,056,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DBZ Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.76,0:54:48.36,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've done all{\i0}\N{\i1}that needs to be done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.67,0:54:53.80,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the Star of Justice{\i0}\N{\i1}from South Star Six Sacred Fists.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.78,0:55:05.94,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Star of Justice lives{\i0}\N{\i1}for others and dies for others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.75,0:55:09.08,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no regrets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.75,0:55:15.19,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ken, Lin, Bat, Toki, Airi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.79,0:55:18.76,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mamiya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.70,0:55:58.67,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.27,0:56:03.67,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.32,0:56:20.29,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.41,0:56:48.28,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,Rei, I won't forget\Nhow you lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.85,0:56:54.05,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,Like Shin, you'll live\Non in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.47,0:57:14.71,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.92,0:57:24.55,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,What is it, Mamiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.92,0:57:25.89,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,The star...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.29,0:57:28.05,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,I can't see Alcor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.33,0:57:35.89,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,The Death Omen Star\Nhas disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.63,0:57:39.93,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,Rei's love brought\Nus a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.77,0:57:49.44,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei, the Star of Justice{\i0}\N{\i1}from South Star Six Sacred Fists.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.98,0:57:55.28,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your legend{\i0}\N{\i1}will live on forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.49,0:58:05.33,DBZ Standard,057,0,0,0,,{\i1}Farewell, Rei.{\i0}
